    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">The Joy that trembles in her eye</l>
     <l n="2">She bows her meek &amp; humble head</l>
     <l n="3">[...] in silent praise</l>
     <l n="4">[...] beyond the power of Sound.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2">
     <l n="5">[...] and smart beneath the visionary scourge</l>
     <l n="6">â€” 'tis Ridicule &amp; not reproach that wounds</l>
     <l n="7">Their vanity &amp; not their conscience feels</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3">
     <l n="8">A few shall [...]</l>
     <l n="9">The cadence of my song repeat</l>
     <l n="10">&amp; hail thee in my words.</l>
    </lg>
